    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, drain and rinse your <strong>green lentils</strong></p><p>Pat your <strong>cod fillet[s]</strong> dry with<strong> </strong>kitchen paper and season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p>",
