    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained lentils</strong> to the pan and cook for 1-2 min or until everything is combined</p><p>Chop<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>your <strong>creamed</strong> <strong>coconut </strong>roughly (if required!)</p><p>Dissolve the <strong>chopped creamed coconut</strong> and <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> in 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[260ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[350ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> – this is your <strong>coconut stock</strong></p>",
