    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>spinach</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Add the <strong>coconut stock</strong> to the pan along with your <strong>spinach </strong>and cook for 3-4 min or until all the spinach has wilted and the sauce has thickened – these are your <strong>curried lentils</strong></p>",
