    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a separate, large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a large drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>ground</strong> <strong>turmeric</strong> and cook for 30 secs until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>cod fillet[s]</strong> to the pan and cook for 4-5 min on each side or until cooked through – this is your <strong>turmeric cod</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
