    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the cod is cooking, top, tail, peel and grate your <strong>carrot[s]</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>grated carrot</strong> to a bowl with your <strong>nigella seeds</strong>, your <strong>red wine vinegar</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>quick-pickled carrot</strong></p>",
